item.title: Helpp?
item.dc:creator: @d_man103456 d man103456
item.description:
@d_man103456 wrote:

ok for delta it is in clickingmost.java. It just takes a little effort. (Not saying you didnt try) Most teleports for delta have a +misc.random(#) on them which makes you teleport within a certain distance of the coords on the teleport. If you don’t know the case (i dont either right off the back) you best chance would be to press ctrl+f and type in

+misc.random(

and just try the coords. I doubt there should be too many to try because i could will be grouped together for like portals or npcs who teleport you. Which takes them out of the run.
